</div>
          <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#ADMS-06-15-02-0080-fn-0001-ptr" id="ADMS-06-15-02-0080-fn-0001">1</a>
   <p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> and <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Quincy Adams (17671848), son of John and Abigail Adams ]">JQA</abbr> returned to The Hague on this date (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary of John Quincy Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. David Grayson Allen, Robert J. Taylor, and others, Cambridge, 1981. ]">JQA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-03-01-02-0005-0007-0002%20ADMS-print-03-01-02-0005-0007-0003%20ADMS-print-03-01-02-0005-0007-0004%20ADMS-print-03-01-02-0005-0007-0005%20ADMS-print-03-01-02-0005-0007-0006%20ADMS-print-03-01-02-0005-0008-0001%20ADMS-print-03-01-02-0005-0009-0001#ADMS-03-01-02-pb-0176" class="pageNo">1:176</a>).</p>
</div>
          
